---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 504
  - Title: Shekel Hakodesh
    Location: 154
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Trust in God
---
If thou but hast the help of God, the dry wood of the forest will bear
thee fruit, until thou shalt say, ‘Enough’; but if He above be not
with thee, then even the garden-trees will not bring forth, their
fruit they will deny, until thou shalt ask, ‘Where are they?’
